      <title>联合国未能打破银行僵局，利比亚石油产量进一步下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/libyan-oil-flows-slide-further-as-un-fails-to-break-bank-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于联合国主导的谈判未能打破利比亚央行控制权僵局，且僵局已蔓延至利比亚石油行业，利比亚原油出口持续下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/libyan-oil-flows-slide-further-as-un-fails-to-break-bank-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 09:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
